# Code owners for ServerKit.
#
# GitHub automatically requests a review from the listed owner on any PR that
# touches a matching path. Enable "Require review from Code Owners" in branch
# protection to make that review mandatory.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Funding and donation addresses — SECURITY SENSITIVE
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# A swapped crypto address is a well-known open-source supply-chain attack:
# a drive-by PR edits one character in a donation address, it reads as a
# harmless docs tweak, and every subsequent donation goes to the attacker.
# These paths must never be merged without the maintainer reading the diff
# character by character against the wallet.
/.github/FUNDING.yml            @jhd3197
/scripts/generate-funding-qr.mjs @jhd3197
/docs/images/funding/           @jhd3197

# The donation addresses live in the Support section of every README, so any
# change to these files needs the same scrutiny.
/README.md                      @jhd3197
/docs/README.es.md              @jhd3197
/docs/README.pt.md              @jhd3197
/docs/README.zh-CN.md           @jhd3197

